# Zephyr/build artifacts
build/
twister-out*/
zephyrproject*/
*.elf
*.bin
*.hex
*.map
*.uf2
# A Kconfig .config can carry a baked-in CONFIG_APP_WIFI_PSK (build dir or a
# stray twister output), so never commit one.
.config
*.config

# Local Wi-Fi credentials overlay (provides CONFIG_APP_WIFI_SSID/PSK). Never
# commit credentials; scripts/build_wifi.sh includes it only if it is present.
# Repo-wide (not just app/) so a differently placed local conf cannot slip in.
*.local.conf

# Evidence: keep logs but do not accidentally commit huge videos unless intended
evidence/*.mp4
evidence/*.mov

# Not hardware evidence (placeholder meme); replace with a real LCD photo.
evidence/popcat.jpg

# AI-tooling / agent scaffolding — kept locally, not part of the public,
# tool-agnostic repo. A reader without any AI tools can reproduce everything
# from README.md + CONTRIBUTING.md + docs/.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
AGENTS.md
prompts/
docs/adr/0003-claude-code-agent-workflow.md

# Python
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.venv/
